data.title: General MacArthur greeting President Osmena, Manila, Philippines, 1945
data.text: Photograph. U.S. General Douglas MacArthur (left) greeting Philippine President Sergio Osmena. Official Caption: "Rome. 7/11/45--MacArthur greets Osmena--U.S. General of the Army Douglas MacArthur (L) greets Sergio Osmena as the Philippines President arrives in Manila after a five months' visit to Washington to confer on relief and rehabilitation problems for the liberated islands. A nine-man commission of Americans and Filipinos returned with President Osmena to investigate the Philippines postwar economy and rehabilitation including damages to property by the Japanese.--War pool photo through Rome OWI--Approved by appropriate military authority (List A out) 7077." Manila, Philippines. 11 July 1945
